                     <interp inst="t17900224-43-person445" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>The prisoner brought this watch the 16th of January to our house; I lent him eighteen shillings on it; and with the money he took out some wearing apparel.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900224-43-person446">
